Name: Crab Digger
About the game: Crab Digger is a fun arcade game with RPG elements. You have to be in the center of a tropical island and control a funny crab. Pump up your character and try to get as far as possible in an endless variety of earthen blocks. Break all the blocks in the level to go to the next and set a new record! And don't forget to collect coins, because thanks to them you can improve the damage and durability of your pickaxe! Peculiarities: - Nice graphics; - Addictive gameplay; - Relaxing gameplay.
